#### Loading States
- **Skeleton Screens**: Dark gray (#1a1a1a) with subtle shimmer
- **Progress Indicators**: Bright accent color progress bars
- **Pulse Effects**: Subtle pulsing animation for loading states

### Component Styling Guidelines

#### Key Metrics Cards
```css
.metric-card {
  background: #1a1a1a;
  border: 1px solid #333333;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 24px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* Corner brackets */
.metric-card::before,
.metric-card::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 12px;
  height: 12px;
  border: 2px solid #3b82f6;
}

.metric-card::before {
  top: 8px;
  left: 8px;
  border-right: none;
  border-bottom: none;
}

.metric-card::after {
  bottom: 8px;
  right: 8px;
  border-left: none;
  border-top: none;
}
```

